                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7624" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MSL-0101</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">4135 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">审计利剑斩蛀虫，全力赋能乡村兴</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Audits’ Sharp Sword Kills Borers, Fully Supporting Rural Revitalization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王杏芬，王见付，胡琪， 程雪艳，杨雪峰，邓羽南</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆市长寿区审计局</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公共管理和社会组织</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">监察与纪检部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">乡村振兴；虚增投保；虚假理赔；研究型审计；大数据审计；2023百优案例；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Rural revitalization; False increase insurance; False claim settlement; Research audit; Big data audit</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">自党的十九大首次提出乡村振兴战略以来，审计署要求着力监督检查该战略的政策实施、资金投入使用绩效等情况，尤其应关注农业信贷担保、农业保险等资金使用情况。为全面深入贯彻这一精神，2021年，C区审计局对全区政策性农业保险资金开展了专项审计。选取S镇Y村审计的结果发现：涉案村干部和保险公司的业务员合谋，通过虚增投保面积，虚构理赔款，既肥了村干部的腰包，又提升了业务员的业绩，致使国家财政资金严重流失。好在审计利剑及时斩断了这一黑色利益链，确保了国家资金的安全完整。通过分析本案中政策性农业保险资金专项审计团队冲破重重阻力，拨开层层迷雾，最终发现严重违法行为的过程，引导学生学习如何综合运用研究型审计和大数据审计，进行系统研究、综合分析，精准找出贪污蛀虫，从而提升审计质效，全力赋能乡村振兴，最终提升国家治理水平。本案例旨在增强学生对审计职能和作用等理论的理解，培养其灵活运用审计理论分析现实案例的综合能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since the 19th National Congress of the Communist Party of China first put forward the rural revitalization strategy, the National Audit Office has required efforts to supervise and inspect the implementation of the strategy&#39;s policies and the performance of fund investment and use, especially the use of funds such as agricultural credit guarantee and agricultural insurance. In order to fully and deeply implement this spirit, in 2021, the C District Audit Bureau carried out a special audit of the policy-based agricultural insurance funds in the district. The results of the audit of Y village in S Town found that the village cadres involved in the case conspired with the salesman of the insurance company to falsely increase the insured area and make up the claims, which not only enriched the pockets of the village cadres, but also improved the performance of the salesman, resulting in a serious loss of national financial funds. Fortunately, the audit sword cut off this black interest chain in time to ensure the safety and integrity of national funds. Through analyzing the process of the special audit team of policy-based agricultural insurance funds in this case, which broke through many obstacles and cleared layers of fog, and finally found serious illegal acts, students were guided to learn how to comprehensively apply research audit and big data audit, conduct systematic research and comprehensive analysis, and accurately identify corruption borer, so as to improve audit quality and efficiency and fully empower rural revitalization. Finally, the level of national governance will be improved. This case aims to enhance students&#39; understanding of the theory of audit function and role, and cultivate their comprehensive ability to flexibly use audit theory to analyze real cases.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《审计学》、《审计理论与实务》、《政府审计理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">舞弊三因素理论；审计程序；审计监督理论；政府审计与乡村治理、国家治理的关系理论；审计职能和作用理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
